    "Title": "Missing: ~mission(TargetName)",
    "Description": "An upstanding member of the Citizens for Prosperity community, Doctor ~mission(TargetName), was recently abducted by XenoThreat while distributing vital medical supplies to one of our settlements.\n\nThe kidnappers were last seen entering their base at ~mission(Location|Address), but we are uncertain whether they will remain there for long. XenoThreat maintains multiple outposts throughout this system and has been known to swap locations at a moment's notice. \n\nConsidering the danger and the distance you may have to travel, CFP is prepared to offer a substantial reward for determining what happened to Dr. ~mission(TargetName|Last).\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
